#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Projector - Locator of Scientist Compound"
msgid_plural "Hologram Projector - Locator of Scientist Compounds"
msgstr[0] "全息投影仪 - 科学家园区定位器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Projector - Locator of Scientist
#. Compound'}
#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This is a hologram projector which generates an interactive hologram when "
"you activate it. Hologram can talk to you, answer some of your questions, "
"but most importantly, it can locate Scientist Compound"
msgstr "这是一台全息投影仪，激活时会生成交互式全息影像。全息影像可以与你对话，回答你的一些问题，但最重要的是，它能定位科学家园区。"

#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Projector - Locator of Shady Warehouse"
msgid_plural "Hologram Projector - Locator of Shady Warehouses"
msgstr[0] "全息投影仪 - 可疑仓库定位器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Projector - Locator of Shady
#. Warehouse'}
#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This is a hologram projector which generates an interactive hologram when "
"you activate it. Hologram can talk to you, answer some of your questions, "
"but most importantly, it can locate Shady Warehouse"
msgstr "这是一台全息投影仪，激活时会生成交互式全息影像。全息影像可以与你对话，回答你的一些问题，但最重要的是，它能定位可疑仓库。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Steampunk Mod"
msgstr "蒸汽朋克模组"

#. ~ Description for Steampunk Mod
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a variety of steampunk items, enemies and locations inspired by the "
"Arcanum crpg."
msgstr "添加了多种受《奥秘》角色扮演游戏启发的蒸汽朋克物品、敌人和地点。"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Town Resident' for a male character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Town Resident"
msgstr "小镇居民"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Town Resident' for a female character
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Town Resident"
msgstr "小镇居民"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Town Resident' for a male character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Whether through birth or passing by on your travels, you have stumbled upon "
"a quaint little town, seemingly stuck in an odd version of the 19th century."
msgstr "无论是出生于此还是在旅途中经过，你偶然发现了一个古雅的小镇，似乎被困在了一个奇特的19世纪版本中。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Town Resident' for a female character.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Whether through birth or passing by on your travels, you have stumbled upon "
"a quaint little town, seemingly stuck in an odd version of the 19th century."
msgstr "无论是出生于此还是在旅途中经过，你偶然发现了一个古雅的小镇，似乎被困在了一个奇特的19世纪版本中。"

#. ~ Starting location for scenario 'Town Resident'.
#: .\scenario.json
msgctxt "start_name"
msgid "local town"
msgstr "当地小镇"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large bore cartridge"
msgid_plural "large bore cartridges"
msgstr[0] "大口径弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bore cartridge'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and a metallic projectile.  "
"Historically used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The "
"cartridge is larger than most of its type."
msgstr "一种装有黑火药和金属弹丸的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大。"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large bore shot cartridge"
msgid_plural "large bore shot cartridges"
msgstr[0] "大口径霰弹弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bore shot cartridge'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and metallic shot.  Historically "
"used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The cartridge is "
"larger than most of its type."
msgstr "一种装有黑火药和金属霰弹的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大。"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large bore shell"
msgid_plural "large bore shells"
msgstr[0] "大口径炮弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bore shell'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and a metallic projectile.  "
"Historically used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The "
"cartridge is larger than most of its type. Carries an explosive charge."
msgstr "一种装有黑火药和金属弹丸的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大，并携带爆炸装药。"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large bean bore cartridge"
msgid_plural "large bean bore cartridges"
msgstr[0] "大口径豆袋弹弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bean bore cartridge'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and a metallic projectile.  "
"Historically used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The "
"cartridge is larger than most of its type and contains a large beanbag to "
"heavily stun enemies."
msgstr ""
"一种装有黑火药和金属弹丸的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大，内含一个大豆袋，能严重击晕敌人。"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large acid bore cartridge"
msgid_plural "large acid bore cartridges"
msgstr[0] "大口径酸液弹弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large acid bore cartridge'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and a metallic projectile.  "
"Historically used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The "
"cartridge is larger than most of its type and contains an acid bomb to "
"create caustic area denial."
msgstr ""
"一种装有黑火药和金属弹丸的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大，内含一枚酸液炸弹，可制造腐蚀性区域以阻止敌人。"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large bore net cartridge"
msgid_plural "large bore net cartridges"
msgstr[0] "大口径网弹弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bore net cartridge'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and a metallic projectile.  "
"Historically used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The "
"cartridge is larger than most of its type and contains a net to entangle "
"enemies."
msgstr "一种装有黑火药和金属弹丸的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大，内含一张网，可缠住敌人。"

#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid "large bore flame cartridge"
msgid_plural "large bore flame cartridges"
msgstr[0] "大口径火焰弹弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bore flame cartridge'}
#: .\sp_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A paper cartridge containing black powder and a metallic projectile.  "
"Historically used to reload muzzleloaders in a more reasonable time. The "
"cartridge is larger than most of its type and contains a flammable charge to"
" ignite terrain and enemies."
msgstr ""
"一种装有黑火药和金属弹丸的纸质弹壳。历史上用于在更合理的时间内重新装填前装枪。这种弹壳比大多数同类弹壳更大，内含易燃装药，可点燃地形和敌人。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "bowler hat of kinetic diversion"
msgid_plural "bowler hat of kinetic diversions"
msgstr[0] "动能偏转圆顶礼帽"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'bowler hat of kinetic diversion'}.
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "You turn the bowler hat on."
msgstr "你打开了圆顶礼帽。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'bowler hat of kinetic
#. diversion'}.
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "The hat of kinetid diversion's batteries are dead."
msgstr "动能偏转礼帽的电池已耗尽。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bowler hat of kinetic diversion'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'activated bowler hat of kinetic diversion'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A bowler hat with an array of magnetic coils on its perimeter.  The hat can "
"admit an electric field to protect the user when activated, running off of "
"batteries."
msgstr "一顶边缘装有磁线圈阵列的圆顶礼帽。激活时，帽子可以产生电场保护使用者，依靠电池运行。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "activated bowler hat of kinetic diversion"
msgid_plural "activated bowler hat of kinetic diversions"
msgstr[0] "已激活的动能偏转圆顶礼帽"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'activated bowler hat of kinetic
#. diversion'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'activated galvanic motor shoes'}.
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "Turn off"
msgstr "关闭"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'activated bowler hat of kinetic diversion'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'activated galvanic motor shoes'}.
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "The %s flicks off."
msgstr "%s 啪地一声关掉了。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "eye gear"
msgid_plural "eye gears"
msgstr[0] "目镜装备"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'eye gear'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"An armored pair of lenses for sight magnification for those who are both "
"near-sighted and far-sighted.  You can use them to focus sunlight. Increases"
" perception by +1"
msgstr "一副装甲镜片，用于为近视和远视者提供视觉放大。你可以用它们聚焦阳光。感知 +1"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "goggled helmet"
msgid_plural "goggled helmets"
msgstr[0] "护目头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'goggled helmet'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"An armored helmet with goggles affixed to its front. Boosts the user's "
"vision while providing all around protection. Increases perception by +1"
msgstr "一顶前部固定有护目镜的装甲头盔。提升使用者的视野，同时提供全方位保护。感知 +1"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "vision helmet"
msgid_plural "vision helmets"
msgstr[0] "视觉头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vision helmet'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"An armored helmet with a meshed visor affixed to its front. Boosts the "
"user's vision while providing all around protection. Increases perception by"
" +1"
msgstr "一顶前部固定有网状面罩的装甲头盔。提升使用者的视野，同时提供全方位保护。感知 +1"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "charged vambrace"
msgid_plural "charged vambraces"
msgstr[0] "充能护臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'charged vambrace'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A vambrace imbued with a constant electrostatic charge. Gives the wearer "
"minor boosts to speed and dexterity while worn."
msgstr "一个灌注了持续静电电荷的护臂。佩戴时给予穿戴者速度和敏捷度的轻微提升。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "wool jacket"
msgid_plural "wool jackets"
msgstr[0] "羊毛夹克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wool jacket'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A professional-looking wool jacket.  Commonly worn by men in town guards. "
"Features thick wool padding, but is still fairly easy to move in."
msgstr "一件外观专业的羊毛夹克。通常由城镇卫队的男性穿着。采用厚羊毛衬垫，但仍相当便于活动。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "smoking jacket"
msgid_plural "smoking jackets"
msgstr[0] "吸烟夹克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'smoking jacket'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A professional-looking smoking jacket.  Only for the most debonair of men."
msgstr "一件外观专业的吸烟夹克，专为最风度翩翩的男士设计。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "elegant dress"
msgid_plural "elegant dress"
msgstr[0] "优雅礼服"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'elegant dress'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "An elegant-looking dress, fit only for women of the upper class."
msgstr "一件外观优雅的礼服，仅适合上流社会的女性穿着。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "plain dress"
msgid_plural "plain dress"
msgstr[0] "朴素连衣裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'plain dress'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "A fine-looking dress, fit for women of all social classes"
msgstr "一件外观精致的连衣裙，适合所有社会阶层的女性。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "rustic dress"
msgid_plural "rustic dress"
msgstr[0] "乡村风格连衣裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'rustic dress'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A somewhat rough but sturdy dress, equally suited for work on a farm or in a"
" factory."
msgstr "一件略显粗糙但结实的连衣裙，同样适合农场或工厂的工作。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "machined combat plate"
msgid_plural "machined combat plates"
msgstr[0] "机械战斗板甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'machined combat plate'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"Powered by the finest in minute steam engine technology and mechanical "
"computing, this set of machined combat plate is head and shoulders above its"
" peers on the field of battle.."
msgstr "由最精密的微型蒸汽引擎技术和机械计算驱动，这套机械战斗板甲在战场上远超同类装备。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "machined combat helmet"
msgid_plural "machined combat helmets"
msgstr[0] "机械战斗头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'machined combat helmet'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A fully enclosed helmet to work in conjunction with the machined combat "
"plate power armor."
msgstr "一个全封闭式头盔，与机械战斗板甲动力装甲协同工作。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "outdoor dress"
msgid_plural "outdoor dress"
msgstr[0] "户外连衣裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'outdoor dress'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A dress that has been made seemingly for use outdoors, fortified beyond "
"usual feminine work. Includes pockets!"
msgstr "一件似乎专为户外使用设计的连衣裙，加固程度超越通常的女性工作服。包含口袋！"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "mechanical dress"
msgid_plural "mechanical dress"
msgstr[0] "机械连衣裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'mechanical dress'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A dress that has been made seemingly for use outdoors, fortified beyond "
"usual feminine work. Includes pockets! With the addition of a miniature "
"steam engine and motors, this dress's capabilties are boosted far beyond "
"normal levels."
msgstr "一件似乎专为户外使用设计的连衣裙，加固程度超越通常的女性工作服。包含口袋！加上微型蒸汽引擎和马达，这件连衣裙的性能远超普通水平。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "galvanic motor shoes"
msgid_plural "galvanic motor shoess"
msgstr[0] "电驱动马达鞋"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'galvanic motor shoes'}.
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "You turn the motor shoes."
msgstr "你启动了马达鞋。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'galvanic motor shoes'}.
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "The motor shoes batteries are drained."
msgstr "马达鞋的电池耗尽了。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'galvanic motor shoes'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of shoes with attached electric motors near the heels. When "
"activated, the user can accelerate far beyond normal speeds. Run on battery "
"charge."
msgstr "一双在鞋跟附近装有电动马达的鞋子。激活时，使用者可以加速到远超正常速度。依靠电池充电运行。"

#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid "activated galvanic motor shoes"
msgid_plural "activated galvanic motor shoess"
msgstr[0] "已激活的电驱动马达鞋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'activated galvanic motor shoes'}
#: .\sp_armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of shoes with attached electric motors near the heels. When "
"activated, the user can accelerate far beyond normal speeds. The motor shoes"
" are currently active, and running off battery charge."
msgstr "一双在鞋跟附近装有电动马达的鞋子。激活时，使用者可以加速到远超正常速度。马达鞋当前已激活，并依靠电池充电运行。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "physical prowess enhanced"
msgstr "体能增强"

#. ~ Description of effect 'physical prowess enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"Your strength and intelligence have been boosted by the elixir of physical "
"prowess"
msgstr "你的力量和智力已通过体能增强药剂得到提升"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'physical prowess enhanced'.
#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'perception enhanced'.
#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'dexterity enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "You inhale the elixir."
msgstr "你吸入了药剂。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'physical prowess enhanced'.
#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'perception enhanced'.
#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'dexterity enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "The elixir's effect wears off."
msgstr "药剂的效果消失了。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "perception enhanced"
msgstr "感知增强"

#. ~ Description of effect 'perception enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Your perception have been boosted by the tonic of awareness"
msgstr "你的感知已通过警觉药剂得到提升"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "dexterity enhanced"
msgstr "敏捷增强"

#. ~ Description of effect 'dexterity enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Your dexterity have been boosted by the tonic of increased reflexes"
msgstr "你的敏捷已通过反射增强药剂得到提升"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "intelligence enhanced"
msgstr "智力增强"

#. ~ Description of effect 'intelligence enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Your intelligence have been boosted by the mind boosting lozenge"
msgstr "你的智力因思维增强含片而得到提升"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'intelligence enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "You eat the lozenge."
msgstr "你吃下了含片。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'intelligence enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "The lozenge's effect wears off."
msgstr "含片的效果逐渐消退。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "speed enhanced"
msgstr "速度增强"

#. ~ Description of effect 'speed enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Your speed have been boosted by quickdash powder"
msgstr "你的速度因疾驰粉末而得到提升"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'speed enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "You eat the powder."
msgstr "你吃下了粉末。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'speed enhanced'.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "The powder's effect wears off."
msgstr "粉末的效果逐渐消退。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "physical prowess elixir"
msgid_plural "physical prowess elixir"
msgstr[0] "体能灵药"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': 'physical prowess elixir'}.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"You feel your muscles tension and your synapses activate as you drink the "
"elixir."
msgstr "饮下灵药时，你感到肌肉紧绷，神经突触活跃起来。"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'physical prowess elixir'}
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"A strong elixir designed to boost one's strength and intelligence for a "
"short period of time."
msgstr "一种强力灵药，旨在短时间内提升使用者的力量与智力。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Addison's tonic of awareness"
msgid_plural "Addison's tonic of awareness"
msgstr[0] "艾迪森的感知滋补剂"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': "Addison's tonic of
#. awareness"}.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"You feel your eyes dilate, and suddenly the world around you becomes more "
"clear."
msgstr "你感到瞳孔扩张，周围的世界突然变得更加清晰。"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': "Addison's tonic of awareness"}
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"A strong tonic developed by the frenetic doctor Sneed Addison. A drug "
"designed to boost one's perception for a short period of time."
msgstr "由狂热医师斯尼德·艾迪森研发的强力滋补剂。一种旨在短时间内提升使用者感知的药物。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Alfred's tonic of increased reflexes"
msgid_plural "Alfred's tonic of increased reflexes"
msgstr[0] "阿尔弗雷德的反射增强滋补剂"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': "Alfred's tonic of increased
#. reflexes"}.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"You feel your nerves calm down considerably, as if your dexterity was now "
"heightened beyond normal levels."
msgstr "你感到神经显著平静下来，仿佛灵巧度已提升至超越正常水平。"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': "Alfred's tonic of increased reflexes"}
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"After imbibing the tonic of Alfred Mogus, the user will soon see marked "
"increase in their dexterity for a period of time."
msgstr "服用阿尔弗雷德·莫古斯的滋补剂后，使用者的灵巧度将在一段时间内显著提升。"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Boyce's patented mind boosting lozenge"
msgid_plural "Boyce's patented mind boosting lozenge"
msgstr[0] "博伊斯专利思维增强含片"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': "Boyce's patented mind
#. boosting lozenge"}.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"You feel your thoughts appear more rapidly and with far more clarity, as if "
"your intelligence was now heightened beyond normal levels."
msgstr "你感到思维涌现得更快且更为清晰，仿佛智力已提升至超越正常水平。"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': "Boyce's patented mind boosting lozenge"}
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"A drug purported to increase the intelligence of the user beyond normal "
"levels, beware though, as repeated use can cause health problems!"
msgstr "一种据称能提升使用者智力至超越正常水平的药物，但需警惕，反复使用可能导致健康问题！"

#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid "Thorpe's certified quick-dash powder"
msgid_plural "Thorpe's certified quick-dash powder"
msgstr[0] "索普认证疾驰粉末"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': "Thorpe's certified quick-
#. dash powder"}.
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"You feel your muscles fill with energy, every tendon tensions up with power!"
msgstr "你感到肌肉充满能量，每一根肌腱都因力量而紧绷！"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': "Thorpe's certified quick-dash powder"}
#: .\sp_drugs.json
msgid ""
"A blueish-white powder that when ingested, drastically increases a user's "
"mobility! Be warned, as continued use can be detrimental to one's health."
msgstr "一种蓝白色粉末，服用后可大幅提升使用者的机动性！请注意，持续使用可能对健康有害。"

#: .\sp_items.json
msgid "auto skeleton key"
msgid_plural "auto skeleton keys"
msgstr[0] "自动万能钥匙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'auto skeleton key'}
#: .\sp_items.json
msgid ""
"This is an artisan-crafted set of picks and torsion wrenches made from fine "
"steel. Equipped with spring-tensioned tumbler mechanisms to ease "
"lockpicking."
msgstr "这是一套由精钢制成、工匠打造的撬锁工具与扭力扳手。配备弹簧张力锁芯机构，以简化开锁过程。"

#: .\sp_items.json
msgid "Guide on Mechanical Knowledge"
msgid_plural "copies ofGuide on Mechanical Knowledge"
msgstr[0] "机械知识指南"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Guide on Mechanical Knowledge', 'str_pl':
#. 'copies ofGuide on Mechanical Knowledge'}
#: .\sp_items.json
msgid ""
"An advanced guide on topics that seem relevant to mechanical engineering, "
"electrical engineering and chemistry. Often written in somewhat stilted 19th"
" century prose."
msgstr "一本关于机械工程、电气工程与化学相关主题的高级指南。常以略显生硬的19世纪散文风格撰写。"

#: .\sp_items.json
msgid "auto safecracker device"
msgid_plural "auto safecracker devices"
msgstr[0] "自动保险柜破解装置"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'auto safecracker device'}
#: .\sp_items.json
msgid ""
"This is an mechanical diaphragm assisted safecracking device. Place on the "
"safe and use to your heart's content! For legal usage only"
msgstr "这是一台机械隔膜辅助的保险柜破解装置。将其置于保险柜上即可随心使用！仅限合法用途"

#: .\sp_items.json
msgid "miniaturized steam engine"
msgid_plural "miniaturized steam engines"
msgstr[0] "微型蒸汽引擎"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'miniaturized steam engine'}
#: .\sp_items.json
msgid ""
"A miniature, steam engine.  An integrated boiler burns coal to heat water "
"into steam, driving a reciprocating shaft.  A condenser recaptures the "
"water, making this a closed cycle system. Commonly used in machined power "
"armor or mechanized automatons."
msgstr "一台微型蒸汽机。其内置锅炉燃烧煤炭将水加热为蒸汽，驱动往复轴运转。冷凝器回收水分，构成封闭循环系统。常用于机械动力装甲或机械化自动机。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "melee gangster"
msgid_plural "melee gangsters"
msgstr[0] "近战帮派分子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'melee gangster'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A criminal who has been hardened by years of conflict in the slums of "
"industrial districts. This one is sporting a pistol of some kind."
msgstr "在工业区贫民窟历经多年冲突磨砺的罪犯。此人正炫耀着某种手枪。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "ranged gangster"
msgid_plural "ranged gangsters"
msgstr[0] "远程帮派分子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ranged gangster'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A criminal who has been hardened by years of conflict in the slums of "
"industrial districts. This one is sporting a knife of some kind."
msgstr "在工业区贫民窟历经多年冲突磨砺的罪犯。此人正炫耀着某种刀具。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "The pistol fires with a loud pop!"
msgstr "手枪发出响亮的爆鸣声！"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "Mad Scientist"
msgid_plural "Mad Scientists"
msgstr[0] "疯狂科学家"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mad Scientist'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A scientist who has honed their craft through study over decades. They've "
"gone a bit mad though, and will have no qualms with killing you."
msgstr "通过数十年钻研磨砺技艺的科学家。但他们已陷入某种疯狂，对杀害你毫无顾忌。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "mechanical arachnid"
msgid_plural "mechanical arachnids"
msgstr[0] "机械蛛形机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mechanical arachnid'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"An insectoid robot the size of a small dog, designed for home security.  "
"Armed with two large steel incisors, it can clatter across the ground with "
"great speed."
msgstr "一种小型犬尺寸的昆虫形态机器人，专为家庭安防设计。配备两枚钢制巨颚，能以极快速度在地面疾行。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "broken mechnical arachnid"
msgid_plural "broken mechnical arachnids"
msgstr[0] "损坏的机械蛛形机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken mechnical arachnid'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A broken mechnaical arachnid, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be "
"gutted for spare parts."
msgstr "一台损坏的机械蛛形机，现已报废静止。可拆解获取备用零件。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "inactive mechanical arachnid"
msgid_plural "inactive mechanical arachnids"
msgstr[0] "未激活的机械蛛形机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive mechanical arachnid'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fixed inactive mechanical arachnid'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"An insectoid robot the size of a small dog, designed for home security.  "
"Armed with two large steel incisors, it can clatter across the ground with "
"great speed. It's currently inactive but ready to be deployed."
msgstr "一种小型犬尺寸的昆虫形态机器人，专为家庭安防设计。配备两枚钢制巨颚，能以极快速度在地面疾行。当前处于未激活状态，但可随时部署。"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "fixed inactive mechanical arachnid"
msgid_plural "fixed inactive mechanical arachnids"
msgstr[0] "修复的未激活机械蛛形机"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "mechanical automaton"
msgid_plural "mechanical automatons"
msgstr[0] "机械自动机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mechanical automaton'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Among the fiercest designs to be borne from the mechanical computing "
"revolution, the automaton is a fearsome weapon of war. Watch out for its "
"scythe blades!"
msgstr "作为机械计算革命催生的最凶悍设计之一，自动机是令人胆寒的战争兵器。当心它的镰刃！"

#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid "broken mechanical automaton"
msgid_plural "broken mechanical automatons"
msgstr[0] "损坏的机械自动机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken mechanical automaton'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"A broken automaton, now wrecked and motionless.  It could be gutted for "
