#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive mechanical automaton'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fixed inactive mechanical automaton'}
#: .\sp_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Among the fiercest designs to be borne from the mechanical computing "
"revolution, the automaton is a fearsome weapon of war. Watch out for its "
