#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Engineer of Mechanics"
msgstr "机械工程师"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Engineer of Mechanics"
msgstr "机械工程师"

#. ~ Profession (male Engineer of Mechanics) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Ever since you were young and gazed upon the great steam engines of your "
"city's local industrial district, you've dreamed of mastering the complex "
"world behind materials and their motion. After years of devotion, you "
"achieved your dream and became well versed in the mechanical sciences."
msgstr "自年少时凝望城市工业区宏伟蒸汽机的那一刻起，你便梦想掌握物质与其运动背后的复杂世界。经年钻研后，你终成所愿，精通机械科学。"

#. ~ Profession (female Engineer of Mechanics) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Ever since you were young and gazed upon the great steam engines of your "
"city's local industrial district, you've dreamed of mastering the complex "
"world behind materials and their motion. After years of devotion, you "
"achieved your dream and became well versed in the mechanical sciences."
