#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Chemistry Practitioner"
msgstr "化学实践者"

#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Chemistry Practitioner"
msgstr "化学实践者"

#. ~ Profession (male Chemistry Practitioner) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Whether you were from a working class neighborhood or the halls of high "
"society, people around you had more than a passing interest in various "
"substances. You on the other hand, were far more interested in the science "
"of chemisty than imbibing various spirits and drugs."
msgstr "无论出身工人街区还是上流社会，周遭人们对各类物质的兴趣皆不止于浅尝。而你却远比对畅饮烈酒或沉迷药物更痴迷于化学科学。"

#. ~ Profession (female Chemistry Practitioner) description
#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Whether you were from a working class neighborhood or the halls of high "
"society, people around you had more than a passing interest in various "
"substances. You on the other hand, were far more interested in the science "
