#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Perhaps out of wanderlust or a desire to protect your fellow townsfolk, you "
"decided to enlist in the town's local military. With only a few months of "
"training, you don't know much about the art of warfare yet."
msgstr "或许是出于漫游的渴望，或是保护镇上同胞的愿望，你决定加入当地的城镇军队。仅经过几个月的训练，你对战争艺术还知之甚少。"

