#: .\sp_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"A budding interest in steam powered vehicles soon blossomed into a deep love"
" of travel. With your hands at the wheel of your trusty steam autocarriage, "
"you drive off into another adventure into the unknown."
msgstr "对蒸汽动力车辆初生的兴趣很快发展成对旅行的深深热爱。手握你信赖的蒸汽汽车方向盘，你驶向未知的又一次冒险。"

